messages.message:
Baa!*** :sheep: feedback

I noticed in `pre-prod: 24.32.2` that when managing user roles from within the `Organization` members page, there's no explicit read out/rendering of which account (identified by account email address) is currently being configured. I was thinking it could be nice to have the user's email address on the pop-up box just to make sure we've targeted the correct one.

_Note*: Translates roughly to: "Hi!_ :wave: _"_
Thanks Brian, I'll likely update this for 24.36!
